@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

## POST /books - 書籍登録（正常系）
### 手順1: 著者登録（このリクエストを先に実行）
# @name createAuthor
POST {{baseUrl}}/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "夏目漱石",
  "birthDate": "1867-02-09"
}

###

### 手順2: 書籍登録（createAuthor のレスポンスから authorId を自動取得）
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "吾輩は猫である",
  "price": 1500,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": [{{createAuthor.response.body.$.id}}]
}

###

### POST /books - 書籍登録（正常系: 複数著者）
# @name createAuthor2
POST {{baseUrl}}/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "森鴎外",
  "birthDate": "1862-01-19"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "共著書籍",
  "price": 2000,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": [{{createAuthor.response.body.$.id}}, {{createAuthor2.response.body.$.id}}]
}

###

### POST /books - 書籍登録（バリデーションエラー: title が空文字）
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "price": 1500,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": [{{createAuthor.response.body.$.id}}]
}

###

### POST /books - 書籍登録（バリデーションエラー: price が負の値）
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "吾輩は猫である",
  "price": -1,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": [{{createAuthor.response.body.$.id}}]
}

###

### POST /books - 書籍登録（バリデーションエラー: authorIds が空）
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "吾輩は猫である",
  "price": 1500,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": []
}

###

### POST /books - 書籍登録（バリデーションエラー: authorIds が null）
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "吾輩は猫である",
  "price": 1500,
  "published": false
}

###

### PUT /books/{id} - 書籍更新（正常系）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "新しいタイトル",
  "price": 2000,
  "published": true,
  "authorIds": [1]
}

###

### PUT /books/{id} - 書籍更新（エラー: 出版済みから未出版への変更は不可）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "新しいタイトル",
  "price": 2000,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": [1]
}

###

### PUT /books/{id} - 書籍更新（エラー: 存在しない書籍ID）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "新しいタイトル",
  "price": 2000,
  "published": false,
  "authorIds": [1]
}

###
